Wei.

99
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:50,270
I really didn't expect Yuan Xia
to agree to go abroad.

100
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:54,040
She did this to set my mind at ease.

101
00:05:56,830 --> 00:05:58,430
We can't delay any longer with Xi Kun.

102
00:05:58,430 --> 00:05:59,920
When do you plan to act?

103
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,040
As soon as Yuan Xia leaves,
we'll take action.

104
00:06:02,510 --> 00:06:05,000
I can't give him any chance
to target Yuan Xia.

105
00:06:05,270 --> 00:06:06,720
If Yuan Xia finds out,

106
00:06:06,730 --> 00:06:08,000
