107
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,480
She thinks
you've finally learned to open up,

108
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:13,920
but here you are,
telling half-truths and hiding the rest.

109
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,680
I just hope that this time,

110
00:06:16,950 --> 00:06:19,240
I can completely change her fate.

111
00:06:24,510 --> 00:06:25,310
By the way...

112
00:06:26,190 --> 00:06:28,480
Once Yuan Xia signs this will,

113
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,920
we'll need photocopies of your IDs

114
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,750
and signatures as witnesses.

115
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:33,830
There's no way Yuan Xia
will sign this will.

116
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,920
She won't know it's a will.

117
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,040
I know her current study progress

118
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:42,870
and the new words she's learned.

119
00:06:43,140 --> 00:06:45,390
She doesn't recognize
any of the important words on it.

120
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,360
Wei.

121
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,240
Ni Ning.

122
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,950
After you sign,

123
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:52,200
quickly take it
to the lawyer for notarization.

124
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:00,240
When is she leaving?

125
00:07:00,340 --> 00:07:01,450
The day after tomorrow.

126
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,310
All right, I'll be off.

127
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,600
Where are you going?

128
