130
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,810
Yuan Xia usually
doesn't have an umbrella.

131
00:07:13,820 --> 00:07:14,770
I'm going to pick her up.

132
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,040
Hello.

133
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,600
Hello.

134
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,430
Why are you here?

135
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,120
I'm here to pick you up.

136
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,000
These are the documents

137
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,600
