138
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,600
You need to sign them.

139
00:08:06,270 --> 00:08:07,870
It's all in French.

140
00:08:08,510 --> 00:08:11,390
I only recognize two words on this page.

141
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,310
It's even worse on the back.

142
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:19,800
I hadn't seen any of these words

143
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,390
when I studied.

144
00:08:22,750 --> 00:08:23,570
Take it slow.

145
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,070
When you get abroad and are immersed

146
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:26,950
in the language, you'll learn faster.

147
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:28,510
I've reviewed all of this for you.

148
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,510
Just sign it.

149
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:32,790
Okay.

150
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:36,880
Yuan Xia.

151
00:08:36,910 --> 00:08:37,460
(Yuan Xia)

152
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,390
Why is it still raining?

153
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:47,000
Luckily, you came.

154
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:50,320
Remember to check the weather forecast

155
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,270
